    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghostly Acres</strong> is an incremental hotel management game that lets you play at your own pace.  Keep a bunch of guests to maximize income or just a few to plan out your next build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mel inherited the manor from her Uncle a few months ago. Unfortunately, he still owes <i>a lot</i> of coins to the bank. Oh, and it's <i>haunted</i> by Flip the not-so-spooky Ghost! Determined to keep their home, Mel and Flip decided to team up. With your help, they can pay off the bank for good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build</strong> beds plus food, drink, and entertainment machines to keep visitors arriving and spending. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/c9323e9ba01df856c6fd1697cffe471a.poster.avif?t=1763826207\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/c9323e9ba01df856c6fd1697cffe471a.webm?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/c9323e9ba01df856c6fd1697cffe471a.mp4?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> coins, gems, and ectoplasm from machines and beds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/d7c90c85e45221355df3237ab29a0f65.poster.avif?t=1763826207\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/d7c90c85e45221355df3237ab29a0f65.webm?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/d7c90c85e45221355df3237ab29a0f65.mp4?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong> Mel, Flip, and other abilities to run more efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/df14513135179a5bd4f59b16a8717864.poster.avif?t=1763826207\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/df14513135179a5bd4f59b16a8717864.webm?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/df14513135179a5bd4f59b16a8717864.mp4?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow</strong> the inn by cleaning off dirty tiles to open up more building space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/6acc7bd8127f6eebd45b9f8a063addbc.poster.avif?t=1763826207\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/6acc7bd8127f6eebd45b9f8a063addbc.webm?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336610/extras/6acc7bd8127f6eebd45b9f8a063addbc.mp4?t=1763826207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
